.Dd December 19, 2022
.Dt ISALPHA 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm isalpha ,
.Nm isalpha_l
.Nd alphabetic character test
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In ctype.h
.Ft int
.Fn isalpha "int c"
.Ft int
.Fn isalpha_l "int c" "locale_t loc"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn isalpha
and
.Fn isalpha_l
functions test for any character for which
.Xr isupper 3 ,
.Xr isupper_l 3
or
.Xr islower 3 ,
.Xr islower_l 3
is true.
The value of the argument must be representable as an
.Vt "unsigned char"
or the value of
.Dv EOF .
.Pp
